snippet.title: Whisker Squadron: Survivor Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Whisker Squadron: Survivor, the first game in the Whisker Squadron universe. A roguelite corridor shooter with a focus on surviving in a continuous world against increasingly difficult waves of robot bugs. Demo on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2140100/Whisker_Squadron_Survivor/
